data.description: This house has more extras that any I have listed in awhile! It has 3 bedrooms 2 baths and a metal roof. Also has a 24 X 24 metal insulated detached garage that is large enough for a shop area, too. It is wired for 110/220. There is a metal 8 X 16 insulated storage and it is wired for 110/220 also. All wiring to the house; cable, phone and electric is underground. It has a concrete patio with poles to build a roof.The home had new wiring in 2002 with all Romex all copper with ground. It has a new breaker box as well. New windows were installed in 2006 and it has 2" wooden blinds throughout. Inside the home is spic and span clean and has been completely repainted. There is new vinyl plank flooring in the kitchen and utility. Speaking of the kitchen, it boasts beautiful all wood cabinets installed in 2005.It has 2 water heaters, one gas and one electric. This one is ready to move in, folks! Don't miss it for only $135,000. Call Sharon Youngblood for more information at 806 759-9811.
